lynx - screenshot utility
=========================
lynx is a simple screenshot utility for x.

Requirements
------------
lynx requires libpng, libxcb and its extensions, libxkbcommon, and xclip.

Installation
------------
lynx comes with a Makefile and config.mk file for configurable building and
testing.  Edit the latter to match your local setup (lynx is installed into the
/usr/local namespace by default, you may need to modify your $PATH).

lynx can be built and installed with the following command (run as root):

    make clean install

